  ('6da72fa1-8533-4fd9-8fe2-e9311b14068e-ex1', '6da72fa1-8533-4fd9-8fe2-e9311b14068e', 'liberation', 'The city celebrated its liberation.', '这座城市庆祝解放。'),
  ('6da72fa1-8533-4fd9-8fe2-e9311b14068e-ex2', '6da72fa1-8533-4fd9-8fe2-e9311b14068e', 'liberation', 'The liberation of the archives transformed scholarship on the period.', '档案的解禁彻底改变了对那个时期的研究。'),
  ('ecd14392-9d20-4996-9a97-41238961a453-ex1', 'ecd14392-9d20-4996-9a97-41238961a453', 'lifelong', 'They are lifelong friends.', '他们是一辈子的朋友。'),
  ('ecd14392-9d20-4996-9a97-41238961a453-ex2', 'ecd14392-9d20-4996-9a97-41238961a453', 'lifelong', 'Repeated violations earned the offender a lifelong industry ban.', '屡次违规使该违规者被终身禁入该行业。'),
  ('32bdc310-2dd8-46f7-a84f-47674ac09a21-ex1', '32bdc310-2dd8-46f7-a84f-47674ac09a21', 'linear', 'The story follows a linear timeline.', '故事按线性时间线展开。'),
