  ('fc7ab410-8338-4ee4-8a23-0755b55378bb-ex1', 'fc7ab410-8338-4ee4-8a23-0755b55378bb', 'linger', 'The smell of bread lingered in the kitchen.', '面包的香味在厨房里久久不散。'),
  ('fc7ab410-8338-4ee4-8a23-0755b55378bb-ex2', 'fc7ab410-8338-4ee4-8a23-0755b55378bb', 'linger', 'Doubts about the certification lingered long after the formal clearance.', '在正式放行之后，对该认证的疑虑仍久久未消。'),
