  ('baedeba2-1fb1-4270-a47a-176da4bda023-ex1', 'baedeba2-1fb1-4270-a47a-176da4bda023', 'literacy', 'The charity promotes child literacy.', '这家慈善机构推动儿童识字。'),
  ('baedeba2-1fb1-4270-a47a-176da4bda023-ex2', 'baedeba2-1fb1-4270-a47a-176da4bda023', 'literacy', 'Financial literacy requirements accompany the marketing of complex products.', '复杂产品的营销须配套金融素养要求。'),
  ('35180ee5-5892-4afd-8057-81f7472c2e15-ex1', '35180ee5-5892-4afd-8057-81f7472c2e15', 'litter', 'Don''t litter in the park.', '不要在公园乱扔垃圾。'),
