  ('043dbd25-0025-4eea-bf0a-14a7f294d119-ex2', '043dbd25-0025-4eea-bf0a-14a7f294d119', 'lord', 'The law lords'' ruling redefined the boundaries of sovereign immunity.', '上议院法官的裁决重新界定了主权豁免的边界。'),
  ('f3757dd5-87da-43a2-9c81-d3a2b4335d31-ex1', 'f3757dd5-87da-43a2-9c81-d3a2b4335d31', 'lottery', 'He won a small prize in the lottery.', '他中了一个小额彩票奖。'),
  ('f3757dd5-87da-43a2-9c81-d3a2b4335d31-ex2', 'f3757dd5-87da-43a2-9c81-d3a2b4335d31', 'lottery', 'The licensing of the national lottery was tendered competitively.', '国家彩票的经营牌照通过竞争性招标授予。'),
  ('22788666-a13b-4152-9abf-4c2976ef4299-ex1', '22788666-a13b-4152-9abf-4c2976ef4299', 'loudly', 'The fans cheered loudly.', '球迷们大声欢呼。'),
