  ('1a103d83-7c0f-4ac5-bbb5-3d7a740ef091-ex2', '1a103d83-7c0f-4ac5-bbb5-3d7a740ef091', 'luxury', 'The luxury segment proved resilient even as mass demand collapsed.', '即使大众需求崩溃，奢侈品板块依然坚挺。'),
  ('e6d29e25-020a-45ce-a231-d5f819ea6394-ex1', 'e6d29e25-020a-45ce-a231-d5f819ea6394', 'lyric', 'She wrote the lyrics for the song.', '她为这首歌作词。'),
  ('e6d29e25-020a-45ce-a231-d5f819ea6394-ex2', 'e6d29e25-020a-45ce-a231-d5f819ea6394', 'lyric', 'The lyric''s authorship was contested through a decade of litigation.', '这段歌词的著作权归属经历了十年诉讼之争。'),
  ('ac71b345-5a89-4742-8db1-5bbf5c9081fb-ex1', 'ac71b345-5a89-4742-8db1-5bbf5c9081fb', 'machinery', 'The farm bought new machinery.', '农场购置了新机械。'),
  ('ac71b345-5a89-4742-8db1-5bbf5c9081fb-ex2', 'ac71b345-5a89-4742-8db1-5bbf5c9081fb', 'machinery', 'The enforcement machinery proved unequal to the scale of evasion.', '执法机器难以应对如此规模的规避行为。'),
