  ('31bc94a4-68a5-4938-9d8c-b72de224bbf1-ex1', '31bc94a4-68a5-4938-9d8c-b72de224bbf1', 'magnificent', 'The palace is magnificent.', '这座宫殿宏伟壮丽。'),
