  ('eaa42114-e84a-403f-8245-5ad6ada634a7-ex1', 'eaa42114-e84a-403f-8245-5ad6ada634a7', 'mainland', 'The ferry connects the island to the mainland.', '渡轮连接海岛与大陆。'),
