  ('627376a1-65b5-4605-ac63-1701ef0a5252-ex2', '627376a1-65b5-4605-ac63-1701ef0a5252', 'subsequently', 'The clause was subsequently held void for inconsistency with the statute.', '该条款后来因与法规相抵触而被判无效。'),
  ('bf64f20f-5485-4416-9126-e67f2139fe27-ex1', 'bf64f20f-5485-4416-9126-e67f2139fe27', 'substitute', 'Use honey as a substitute for sugar.', '用蜂蜜代替糖。'),
