  ('54d1745a-0fa7-4075-a814-c1a6b25a64c0-ex2', '54d1745a-0fa7-4075-a814-c1a6b25a64c0', 'subway', 'The subway expansion was financed through dedicated municipal bonds.', '地铁扩建通过专项市政债券融资。'),
