  ('6e6221a5-5f99-4d16-8abc-9ca207cc00c2-ex1', '6e6221a5-5f99-4d16-8abc-9ca207cc00c2', 'summarize', 'Can you summarize the article?', '你能概括一下这篇文章吗？'),
