  ('c951781f-464d-4de0-b715-18f922c4548e-ex2', 'c951781f-464d-4de0-b715-18f922c4548e', 'temporarily', 'The injunction temporarily restrains enforcement pending appeal.', '在上诉期间，该禁令暂时禁止执行。'),
