  ('59380fb7-4c5f-41d6-8b56-62a50b9171d1-ex2', '59380fb7-4c5f-41d6-8b56-62a50b9171d1', 'terrify', 'The penalties are calibrated to terrify would-be violators into compliance.', '这些处罚的设定旨在震慑潜在违规者使其守法。'),
  ('739d8fc6-f46d-4ebb-bf40-460f588d60cc-ex1', '739d8fc6-f46d-4ebb-bf40-460f588d60cc', 'thankfully', 'Thankfully, no one was hurt.', '谢天谢地，没有人受伤。'),
