  ('e44d2ee6-18dd-45ff-9500-637f80cafb11-ex1', 'e44d2ee6-18dd-45ff-9500-637f80cafb11', 'theatrical', 'The play was a theatrical triumph.', '这部话剧在戏剧上大获成功。'),
  ('e44d2ee6-18dd-45ff-9500-637f80cafb11-ex2', 'e44d2ee6-18dd-45ff-9500-637f80cafb11', 'theatrical', 'Counsel''s theatrical objections served to obscure the substantive deficiencies.', '律师夸张的反对意见转移了人们对实质性缺陷的注意。'),
