  ('daac6f09-ab3e-4f73-b218-f945c411e4d3-ex2', 'daac6f09-ab3e-4f73-b218-f945c411e4d3', 'wildlife', 'The convention restricts trade in wildlife threatened with extinction.', '该公约限制濒临灭绝的野生动物贸易。'),
