  ('ff306bd5-d536-4aa0-816d-247e45a54ad6-ex1', 'ff306bd5-d536-4aa0-816d-247e45a54ad6', 'worship', 'They gather for worship on Sundays.', '他们周日聚会做礼拜。'),
  ('ff306bd5-d536-4aa0-816d-247e45a54ad6-ex2', 'ff306bd5-d536-4aa0-816d-247e45a54ad6', 'worship', 'The charter protects freedom of worship against state interference.', '宪章保护宗教礼拜自由不受国家干预。'),
  ('3205f7fa-d47f-487b-8d19-9dd5eb499cb0-ex1', '3205f7fa-d47f-487b-8d19-9dd5eb499cb0', 'worst', 'That was the worst movie ever.', '那是有史以来最糟糕的电影。'),
  ('3205f7fa-d47f-487b-8d19-9dd5eb499cb0-ex2', '3205f7fa-d47f-487b-8d19-9dd5eb499cb0', 'worst', 'The crisis represented the worst institutional failure in a generation.', '这场危机是一代人以来最严重的机构失灵。'),
