  ('4c8edd10-25c4-469f-b154-d02851e878f7-ex2', '4c8edd10-25c4-469f-b154-d02851e878f7', 'worthwhile', 'The reform proved worthwhile despite its considerable transition costs.', '尽管过渡成本不菲，这项改革仍被证明是值得的。'),
