  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005510-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005510', 'timeline', 'Let''s agree on a timeline for the project.', '我们来定一个项目时间表吧。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005510-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005510', 'timeline', 'The implementation timeline proved far too ambitious in retrospect.', '事后看来，这份实施时间表定得过于激进。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005511-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005511', 'sync', 'Let''s have a quick sync tomorrow.', '明天我们快速对齐一下吧。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005511-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005511', 'sync', 'The replicas fell out of sync, serving stale data to clients.', '各副本失去同步，向客户端返回了过时的数据。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005512-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005512', 'blocker', 'Is there any blocker stopping you?', '有什么东西卡住你了吗？'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005512-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005512', 'blocker', 'The licensing dependency emerged as the critical blocker for launch.', '许可证依赖成了上线的关键阻塞项。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005513-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005513', 'tradeoff', 'There is always a tradeoff between cost and quality.', '成本与质量之间总要有所取舍。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005513-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005513', 'tradeoff', 'The design accepts a latency tradeoff in exchange for stronger consistency.', '该设计接受延迟上的取舍，以换取更强的一致性。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005514-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005514', 'kickoff', 'The project kickoff is on Monday.', '项目启动会在周一。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005514-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005514', 'kickoff', 'The kickoff meeting clarified ownership before any code was written.', '启动会议在编写代码之前就厘清了职责归属。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005515-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005515', 'handoff', 'The handoff between shifts went smoothly.', '两班之间的交接很顺利。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005515-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005515', 'handoff', 'A botched handoff left the incident without a clear owner overnight.', '一次糟糕的交接使该事故一夜之间无人明确负责。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005516-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005516', 'demo', 'Can you give me a quick demo?', '你能给我快速演示一下吗？'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005516-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005516', 'demo', 'The demo concealed edge cases the production system could not handle.', '演示掩盖了生产系统无法处理的边界情况。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005517-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005517', 'prioritize', 'Let''s prioritize the urgent tasks.', '我们先处理紧急任务。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005517-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005517', 'prioritize', 'The team must prioritize the security fix over the planned feature work.', '团队必须把安全修复置于既定的功能开发之上。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005518-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005518', 'reschedule', 'Can we reschedule the meeting?', '我们能改期开会吗？'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005518-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005518', 'reschedule', 'The launch was rescheduled pending resolution of the licensing blocker.', '上线被推迟，以待许可证阻塞项解决。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005519-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005519', 'retrospective', 'We hold a retrospective after each sprint.', '每个冲刺结束后我们都开回顾会。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005519-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005519', 'retrospective', 'The retrospective surfaced process failures the postmortem had overlooked.', '回顾会议揭示了事后复盘所遗漏的流程缺陷。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005520-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005520', 'onboarding', 'My onboarding took a whole week.', '我的入职流程花了整整一周。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005520-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005520', 'onboarding', 'Streamlined onboarding cut the time to first contribution by half.', '精简的入职流程使新人首次贡献的时间缩短了一半。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005521-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005521', 'overview', 'She gave a brief overview of the plan.', '她简要介绍了一下计划。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005521-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005521', 'overview', 'The overview omitted risks material to any informed decision.', '这份概述遗漏了对任何知情决策都至关重要的风险。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005522-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005522', 'mitigation', 'Wearing a mask is one mitigation.', '戴口罩是一种缓解措施。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005522-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005522', 'mitigation', 'The risk mitigation plan must be activated at the first warning sign.', '风险缓解方案必须在出现首个警示信号时启动。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005523-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005523', 'contingency', 'Always have a contingency plan.', '永远要有应急预案。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005523-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005523', 'contingency', 'The contingency reserves proved wholly inadequate to the shock.', '应急储备被证明完全不足以应对这次冲击。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005524-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005524', 'clarification', 'I need a clarification on this point.', '这一点我需要澄清一下。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005524-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005524', 'clarification', 'The ruling provides welcome clarification of a long-contested question.', '该裁决对一个长期争议的问题作出了令人欢迎的澄清。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005525-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005525', 'regards', 'Give my regards to your family.', '代我向你家人问好。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005525-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005525', 'regards', '"Kind regards," the letter closed, before the contested signature.', '信件以“此致敬礼”结尾，随后是那个有争议的签名。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005526-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005526', 'sincerely', 'Yours sincerely, Anna.', '安娜敬上。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005526-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005526', 'sincerely', 'The minister sincerely regretted failures occurring under his stewardship.', '部长对其任内发生的失误深表遗憾。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005527-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005527', 'kindly', 'Kindly close the door behind you.', '请随手关门。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005527-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005527', 'kindly', 'Applicants are kindly requested to submit all documents in duplicate.', '敬请申请人将所有文件一式两份提交。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005528-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005528', 'tentative', 'We made a tentative plan for Saturday.', '我们为周六定了个暂定的计划。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005528-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005528', 'tentative', 'The tentative agreement remained subject to formal ratification.', '这份暂定协议仍有待正式批准。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005529-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005529', 'inconvenience', 'Sorry for the inconvenience.', '给您带来不便，敬请谅解。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005529-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005529', 'inconvenience', 'The notice apologized for the inconvenience without conceding liability.', '通知就造成的不便致歉，但未承认责任。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005530-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005530', 'follow-up', 'I have a quick follow-up question.', '我有一个简短的后续问题。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005530-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005530', 'follow-up', 'The follow-up review confirmed that the remediation had been completed.', '后续审查确认整改已经完成。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005531-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005531', 'luggage', 'We checked our luggage at the airport.', '我们在机场托运了行李。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005531-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005531', 'luggage', 'Customs intercepted luggage containing undeclared currency.', '海关截获了装有未申报货币的行李。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005532-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005532', 'snack', 'I had a snack before dinner.', '晚饭前我吃了点零食。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005532-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005532', 'snack', 'The labeling rules govern health claims on packaged snack foods.', '标签规则规范包装零食的健康声明。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005533-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005533', 'microwave', 'Heat the soup in the microwave.', '用微波炉加热汤。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005533-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005533', 'microwave', 'The safety standards apply to every microwave sold within the market.', '安全标准适用于市场上销售的每一台微波炉。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005534-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005534', 'cashier', 'Pay the cashier at the counter.', '到柜台向收银员付款。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005534-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005534', 'cashier', 'The cashier''s testimony placed the suspect at the scene that evening.', '收银员的证词将嫌疑人置于当晚的现场。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005535-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005535', 'haircut', 'I got a haircut yesterday.', '我昨天理了发。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005535-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005535', 'haircut', 'Bondholders accepted a substantial haircut as the price of restructuring.', '债券持有人接受了大幅减记，作为重组的代价。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005536-ex1', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005536', 'sleepy', 'The warm room made me sleepy.', '温暖的房间让我犯困。'),
  ('b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005536-ex2', 'b2606100-0000-4000-8000-000000005536', 'sleepy', 'The sleepy oversight allowed risks to accumulate unchecked for years.', '松懈的监管使风险多年来无人遏制地累积。')
